						<additions>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="owner">Eliyahu ben Yitsḥaḳ Yafet</name>: inscribed, folio 2r.</p>
							<p>Folio 361v: a record of purchase of the manuscript, dated <date calendar="Gregorian">1618</date>, by <name type="person" role="owner">Yitsḥaḳ ben Eliyah ben Avraham ben Simḥah ben Eliyah ha-Zaḳen</name>, witnessed by , Yitsḥaḳ ben Mordekhai and Mordekhai ben Yeshu῾ah. Same folio, underneath: a note of sale of the manuscript, dated <date calendar="Hebrew">5514 </date>(<date calendar="Gregorian">1753</date>), to <name type="person" role="owner">Shelomoh</name>.</p>
							<p>Folio 361v, side margin: a note signed by Mosheh ben Eliya ha-Levi.</p>
						</additions>
